    <detaileddescription>
<para>Inherits from a datamodel object, adding some visual property masks to it. <computeroutput>BaseObjectType</computeroutput> is the datamodel type to inherit from. <computeroutput>Properties...</computeroutput> is the list of properties to add. Each must be a value from a enum marked as <computeroutput><ref refid="structMR_1_1IsVisualizeMaskEnum" kindref="compound">IsVisualizeMaskEnum</ref></computeroutput>. </para>
